      "title": "MRI Hand at Cadabams Diagnostics | Advanced Imaging ",
      "description": "Get a clear view of your hand today. Cadabams Diagnostics offers high-field MRI Hand scans with 1.5T/3T technology, no radiation, and reports in 24 hrs.\n",
